statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `users` where `role` = 1
select `id`, `image`, `book_name`, `exam_id`, `selling_price` from `books` order by `id` desc limit 5
select `id`, `name`, `email`, `phone` from `users` where `role` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 5
select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'ndnmanag_db' and table_name = 'roles'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` = 1 and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\User'

select SUM(order_price + delivery_price) AS sumValue from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-05-01 00:00:00' and `payment_status` = 'paid' group by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) order by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) asc

select MONTH(created_at) as month from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-05-01 00:00:00' and `payment_status` = 'paid' group by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) order by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) asc

select count(id) as totalPerMonth from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-05-01 00:00:00' and `payment_status` = 'paid' group by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) order by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) asc
select SUM(delivery_price + static_fee + fee_value) AS sumValue from `orders` where `created_at` > '2022-10-24 13:01:47' and `payment_status` = 'paid' limit 1
